### 七、代码示例：快速启动一个通用统计任务

```python
# 1. 定义指标
metric = MetricDef(
    name="api.latency.p99",
    metric_type="summary",
    source_type="log",
    source_config={
        "path": "/var/log/myapp/api.log",
        "parse_func": "extract_latency_ms"
    },
    aggregation="p99",
    anchor_policy="sample",    # 每分钟采一个日志片段
    interval=60
)

# 2. 注册并启动采集
collector = StatCollector()
collector.register_metric(metric)
collector.start()

# 3. 查询当前统计值
value, anchor = collector.get_latest("api.latency.p99")
print(f"P99延迟: {value}ms, 可验证锚定: {anchor['replay_key']}")

# 4. 手动验证
replayed = collector.verify("api.latency.p99", anchor_id)
assert abs(replayed - value) < 0.01
```

